dct_description_sm: Geological Survey of Japan ; Drawn by M. Suganuma, Engraved by D. Okamoto, and T. Kobayashi, Toyoco - Engraving office, Tokio.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Shows low water areas, roads, railroads, towns and their approximate area covered, waterways, districts.
Map extends out of frame in lower right to show southern tip of Chiba prefecture.
Part of the Geological Survey of Japan series.
